content: Hotels with 99% occupancy, full AirBnbs, queues in stores in the center of Rio de Janeiro to buy Madonna items, airline companies offering 200 extra flights to Rio de Janeiro, including leaving from Chile and Argentina! Do you know the percentage of taxes from all this that goes back to the government! Return values ​​for the Government around 300 million! Go get informed instead of talking nonsense!
